messages.content: (Just gonna lay down what it looks like here)

Normal Vulpe: Vulpes mindcape was a forest with lanterns and fairy lights in the cherry blossom trees. On the ground was a lake with crystal clear water. There was also a nice spot for sunbathing. However due to her cracks there was a slight uneasy feeling. Like you where always being watched...sometimes....the trees had eyes....
(Hmmmm funfacf, the whole scenery changes when she goes feral)
(Gonna describe that as well)

Feral Vulpe: The second Vulpe goes feral everything becomes darker and bloody and foggy. Vulpe will be laying in the lake, the water now looking like blood. It might be hard to find her due to how foggy it is and the threat of a more feral version of Vulpe wandering around.
Vulpe lay in her lake, unconscious with a strong fog around her. Everything had become so bloody. A more feral Vulpe was awake here and it would be bard to make her go away.
Sanguis jolts up, gasping, somewhere within Vulpes mindscape
Its incredibly hard to see due to the fog but the lake Vulpe is unconscious in has a very slight glow. However....Theres a howl from somewhere within the dense forest....Vulpes feral side....
Slowly standing up, he tries to stumble through the fog, feeling around, towards the glow. Putting his faith into whatever sick twisted god exists out there.
As he was nearing the lake a growl could be heard from close behind him and 2 clawed hands tried to slash him. It was the feral Vulpe.
One out of the two got, him, dodging the other one, he whipped behind him, to face her, his head darting all around while clutching the stricken arm, “S-Shit...”

She giggled at that, a giggle which seemed to echo. She was standing infront of him as the fog cleared up around her. She....looked very messy. Matted fur, wild untamed hair, long nails that had become claws and blood all over her normal outfit. She had a grin on her face, showing off her sharp teeth.

He eyes widened, as he stepped back, gritted teeth, 
For once, Vulpe’s smile and laugh......were.....unsettling, “Damn it...” he tired to look for a way around her...
She took a step forward as he took one back. She giggled again, trying to attack this time. There was a way around her, a short cut Vulpe always had through the trees. It was noticeable to all.
He coughs up a bit of sliver blood at the attack, before gently kicking her away, trying to jump into the trees, his breathing staggering.
Her smile never fell as she watched him jump into the trees. She knew what he wanted and she would just wait by Vulpe and suprise him there.

“I’ll find you Vulpe.....I promise...” as he jumped from tree to tree, trying to find the unconscious kitsune, wiping the blood from his mouth, surveying the surroundings, a unsettled feeling broiling inside....
The fog had sort of cleared up around the unconscious Vulpe making it so Sanguis could see her floating and unconscious. All he would have to do was get her to wake up

Sighing a breath of relief,he took a leap from the tree, stumbling on the land, and wading his way into the water, a hopeful look in his eyes, he started to use the last bit of strength he had to get to her.
Just then, another giggle and a howl. Feral Vulpe lunged for him, giggling all the while. For the first time, the feral side spoke. "What funnnn what funnnnnnn!!!!" The voice....sounded distorted...

He kept dodging, each time his strength getting smaller and smaller, his body starts to shake, “I.....Won’t.....hurt you......no matter how many times you attack...” he takes an step towards feral Vulpe “**I’ll never hurt you! Neither of you!**” Sanguis shouts
Feral Vulpe froze suddenly as another movement entered the water. That shout has begun to wake Vulpe. The feral side growled and retreated. "Yooouuuuuu winnnnnnnn fffooorrrrrr nnooowwwwwww......"
A small smile appeared as the mun rushed to Vulpes side, shaking her “Dummy......wake up.....wake......up..” he clutches his now bleeding forehead....”please...”

She slowly opened her eyes, the mindscape returning to its normal beautiful self. "....Ugh.....Sanguis...? What.... are you doing here....? An-and what happened to you?!" She snapped fully awake after seeing his injuries

“Heh.....your finally awake......it’s a long story....I’ll tell...you later...just a little tired...hah hah....” With a wavering laugh, he collapsed next to her. “Umph...” a dopey smile spreading, maybe because of the blood loss maybe not, who knows, definitely not him

She blinked a bit and dragged him out of the lake they where in and onto the grass. She placed his head on her lap and ran a hand through his hair. "I must of fallen asleep in my mind......last thing I remember is....the...chemical SmELL OH GOD I WENT FERAL DIDNT I."
He giggled, reaching his hands up to her face “Nonono....you....didn’t go feeral....maybe I did.....where are we again...?...” his head snuggled into her lap, yawning.

"Your in my mindscape...." She blushed a bit. He.....was so cute....Would he even remember this when they both woke up? Well....even if he didn't...she would.....so...she leaned her head down and gently kissed his nose

His giggles exploded at the kiss, though once her lips left his nose, he became pouty, “No...nono....put-put them back....my lips, they hurt.....kiss it better....?” Sanguis whined, puppy dog eyes full blown, “pwease?”
Her face became bright red. Fuck it. She couldn't resist and gently kissed him. Would this count as their first kiss??????? Who knows.

He eagerly leaned in, giving purrs of appreciation,  with a few coos of ‘i love you’ slurred in, once their lips separated, he began giggling again, “What-What if....I told you...my lips...didn’t hurt...and I just wanted you....to kiss me..” his giggles evolved into laughing as he cuddled her “ah hah! I have tricked yoooouu!”

She squeaked a bit, face still bright red. She...she really hoped he would remember this....She was absolutely loving the attention and cuddles. This was heaven to her. "Mmmmmmm You are so cute......"
Shes purring loudly now

“You’re like.....a big ol cat....Nono...**kitten**, you’re a....kitten...*my kitten!*” he proudly exclaims, hugging the living daylights out of her, “my adorable kitten......I looovee youuu...Eh heh heh...” he is loopy out of mind, but was that really a problem?

She purred more, happily hugging him back. She was loving this. She may never get to have this kind of attention from him again hut she doesnt really mind. She knows he loves her....Even if hes a little loopy. "Mmmm I love you too~"

“Y’know....what’s funny,,,a while ago....I thought we were both..knocked out on the floor of a store....but now we’re here...I wonder how-how that happened...this place is n-nice though...Waaaay better than mine...” he hummed, snuggling into her fur, “less shadows.....too..”

She sighed "Yeah....We will have to wake up soon though....people are properly worried....But...I really dont wanna wake up cause this is just so nice...." she purred, shifting into her kitsune form and starting to clean his wounds

“It is.....” Sanguis cooed, before he started squirming and laughing loudly from the cleaning, “**Hahah! Ahahah! Y-Yamero! That Ti-Tickles! A-Ah**!” He clutches his sides, happy tears, streaming down.
"Sh-shush.....Let me clean your wounds..." she sighed "It tickles I know but it will help" she kept cleaning his wounds
“U-Uh huh...” calming down, though still sometimes flinching with small giggles “ mph....kitten...” he whined, “how long will this take....?”
"Not very long if you dont squirm. Luckily your wounds arent that deep....." she hummed as she kept cleaning
“Mmmm, okay....” he mumbles, leaning against her, “how do you even.....do that... thingy...”
She tilted her head "What do you mean?" She hummed, finishing uo cleaning the last wound before curling up around him

“Your always......so nice...to me....even when I’m...not the best mun to be around,,.....I thought you....would just give up....but your still here.....” he cuddles into body, his tail once again wrapping around hers

"Well thats cause I can be stubborn when it comes to love. Did you know animals can tell how you feel..? I can tell that you have a big though guy act and I respect that.....I will never give up on you Sanguis.....I love you too much to do so....." She purred, nuzzling his face a bit
"Mmm....When we wake up your going to probably have to keep me unconscious....The chemical smell makes me go feral....." She sighed
“Aw-awww....Ok.......” he pouted, “What if....just I wake up? Or....does that not work like that...”
"Im not sure....But if I wake up, knock me out again ok...? I dont wanna harm anyone...." She nuzzled him again
"Hm...actually...maybe you can try to will yourself awake????" She tilted her head in thought "I wonder who even knew what smells set that side of me off....."
“Well...I saw a funny looking figure while running....” he taps his chin, “I’ll...try to will myself awake....for you!”
She smiled and went into her human form, giving him a quick kiss again "Thank you my little lovebug~" she giggled
“E-Eh?! Did you just compare me to a **Insect!?!**” he puffed, out.

"A lovebug isnt real....Its a nickname I heard humans using for others!!" She hummed "You're so cute when your annoyed~ Im glad I met you y'know? I would of been a pretty lonely kitsune if I never fell in love....I love you so much Sanguis.....Im so happy you came into my life...."
“Ohhhh........b-but I’m not cute! I’m cool!” He huffs “you’re lucky I love so much kitten........” the mun kissed her hand “Well I’m happier that you came into my life!”

Her tails are wagging so much now. This also means her bells are jingling. "Now....As much as I dont want this to end, You need to wake up ok? Wake me as soon as we are far away enough from the store....." She kissed his nose
“Hnnnn....ok.....I promise...” he nods, giving her a small wave and a giggle, before focusing on and only on waking up.
She watched and waited, nervously playing with her hands
Surely enough, his form starts to flicker in an out of reality, before completing disappearing
She sighed a hit "Oh I really hope he remembers all this...." She laid on the grass. "At least _they_ didnt appear....."
Shes vibing for a bit until she hears footsteps "Oh no......which one is it now....." She sat up on high alert, looking around

She spotted a figure watching in the distance and she got nervous. She never liked having to interact with this one......It resembled Saké too much....
(Its the soul shard infused Saké monster UwU.)
She only hoped Sanguis would wake her up soon....
She climbed up a tree to avoid it.....she didnt wanna bother right now.
Vulpe was here again and she waited for Dominus to appear.
Soon enough, Dominus appears with a flourish, interestingly enough she’s in the Velox form, giving her arms a stretch
Vulpe stood up from watching the koi fish in a little pond area once Dominus entered. "Oh! I didn't know you had another form!" She hummed
“Oh we plasma have *many* forms..” her voice Is noticeably more masculine “this form will make things more quicker so we can finish this in a jiffy,” she hums

She nodded "Ill take note of that! But please do be careful....Theres....quite a bit of monsters lurking around....only one out of all of them are friendly....Youll be able to tell which one is friendly though...." Vulpe hummed

Speaking of monsters, one was lurking around nearby.
She nods “I see...well, let’s find the feral you here....hmm...” tapping her feet in thought, Dominus looks around for something, a clue? A monster? Anything that can give an idea.

Vulpe looked around and saw something peering at them from the trees. She went to get a closer look and more eyes joined it, spooking her. "Dominus....I...Im pretty sure some are watching us already....." Shes starring at the tree still
“Huh? Oh!” The plasma turns around to look at the trees, squinting her eyes “Weird looking buggers aren’t they...?” She curiously inquired, approaching the base of it.
One if them stepped out into the light. It looked like Vulpe bht ALOT more matted and messy. It had many, many eyes adn teeth. "O-Oh god...."
Despite the sight, Dominus has a neutral, almost bored expression, “if you’re scared.. hop on my back.”

Vulpe did so. Dominus could feel her shaking...

The monster lunged at them

She dodged the attack quite easily
In fact It almost looked like they blinked in and out of reality for a second 
Appearing behind the monster, she delivers a electricity filled kick to its back

The monster yelped and fell down.

Meanwhile another monster snuck up behind them and grabbed Vulpe, trying to grab her off Dominus
She yelped and tried shaking the monster off, while concentrating on the other one

It was successful in grabbing Vulpe who was struggling to try and get free before it threw her into a tree, knocking her out.

A thick fog began to form, surrounding Vulpe. Feral Vulpe was here.

An echoing giggle was heard as the once beautiful scenery became bloody are dark. 

The monsters had backed off...
Dominus cringed at the attack, knowing it probably hurt. Tensing at the giggle
The fog has become thick and it was hard to see through. Then, came a voice "A neeewwwwww playmatteeeeeee~? Whatttt funnnnnnn~" There was a figure in a tree, watching Dominus now...
“So it’s you...” there was a more....interested? tone in her voice, while stepping towards the figure “quite a curious thing aren’t you dear?” Her tail swayed
She hoped out of the tree, giggling again. She started to circle Dominus, her grin never falling.

She looks over the feral Vulpe as she circles her, giving small mumbles of observance, “similar looking.....sharp teeth...tattered clothes....long hair....interesting...” she taps her chin and ears twitched....perhaps in excitement?
She heard her call her small and didnt like that. She lunged for Dominus, trying to bite her
Almost taken aback by this, she grabs her neck, keeping her at arms distance, while delivering light shocks to it.
She yelps, trying to claw her arms to try and get her off. Shes snarling as she does so

The plasma barely flinches as snow colored blood dripped down her arm, “don’t make this more painful than it has to be for you honey....calm down..” she amplified the intensity of the shocks a bit more, the jewel on the coat glowing brightly
Slowly she starts to calm down, snarling only a small bit now. Shes stopped trying to claw her arms but she clearly doesn't like this one bit
“There...just relax.” She immediately toned down the intensity of it, down to a point where it wasn’t painful, only mildly uncomfortable
Shes glaring at her but has stopped snarling fully now. This might be as relaxed as she'll get
Satisfied with the result, she gently places the kitsune down on solid ground, slowly backing away to give her some space, but also check up on the unconscious vulpe

She watched her with a glare still but didnt try to attack

The fog around Vulpe was still there but once Dominus sas close enough she could see her head was bleeding from where she was thrown inti the tree
“Oh dear.....” she propped up the girl against the tree, wiping the blood with her gloves, it will have to do for now, before lightly shaking her awake, “darling, rise and shine..”
She groaned, slowly opening her eyes. "Ughh....my head....." She mumbled. She sat up some more and looked around. She was suprised to see how bloody her mindscape looked "What the heck....?"
“Ah, you’re awake, I think I found the problem....” she points to the feral version of Vulpe, “she’s not evil....just cranky I presume.”

Vulpe blinked in suprise and went over to inspect the feral version of herself "Huh.....how interesting....Ive never seen this before....." Her tails swayed a bit

Feral Vulpe huffed a bit, glaring at both of them
Vulpe poked the other causing them to growl a bit
“Oh, I suggest you don’t do that...they’re feisty..”

"Huh....So this is what happens when I snap??" She mused, mainly to herself. 'Then....shes probably the reason Sanguis was so loopy after I woke up in here...' That part she thought to herself "So....is there anything else that needs to be done??"
“Yes...Yes probably....I assume you two switch places in who’s in control of your body....” Dominus nods, piecing the ideas together, “I think not, I feel as though we’ve done enough for now.”
Alright. Thank you Dominus.." She smiled at her "I appreciate the help..."
“Once again, you’re family...” she returned the smile tenfold. “We should go now...”
She nodded "Yeah, Sanguis is probably worried......" she hummed
“Uh huh.....” her image disappears from her mindscape
She wills herself awake
Vulpe groans as she wakes up here, now with a missing leg. Her mindscape looks horrible. Everything is wilted and dead. The lake water all muddy and gross. She felt absolutely horrible.....
She curled up into a ball, starting to sob. She was unaware she now had a new mindscape monster to deal with.
Vulpe landed here and was suprised to see her mindscape looked better
All thr trees where sakura trees
She waited to see if Sanguis would show up
(Nya
Sanguis eventually appears, although slightly dazed.
"Puppy? Are you ok?" She asked
“Y-Yeah.” He rubs his temple at the minor headache.

"Alright..." She smiled a bit and gently hugs him, tails wagging "Its nice that its just the 2 of us here....I can flirt with you all I want~" Vulpe giggled a bit "You are my sweet and oh so handsome husband......"
“Mhm..” he squeaked, “A-Ah....”
She giggled, tails wagging "I love that I can call you my husband now...." Shes purring loudly "Though I really do like calling you Puppy~"
She burried her face into his neck, just happy to relax

".....Yknow...whenever I pick up on your scent....its nice....cause I know its you...Makes me happy...its odd I know but....your scent is nice cause I like said, I know its you and knowing its you makes me happy cause I love you so much...."
